{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_05_01",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 新曲のジャケット撮影",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――I-UNITYが終了してしばらく経ち",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Before long I-UNITY ended",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "新曲のジャケット撮影を、私が中心になって進める？\n……どういうことなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Should I take the lead in the new song's CD cover shooting?\n…What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はい。新曲の『SUNNY PEACE for\nYou and Me！』なんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. It's for the new song‚ \"SUNNY PEACE for You and Me!\"…\nI thought that having the members come up with it themselves",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "メンバー自ら考える方が曲に込めた想いを今までより\nもっと強くファンに伝えられるんじゃないかと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "might allow them to convey their feelings in the song\neven more strongly to the fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、それでMV撮影はさくらちゃんに任せたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. So you left the MV shooting to Sakura-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私でいいの？\nさくらちゃんはリーダーだから、ともかく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ is that okay ?\nSakura-chan is the leader‚ after all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんはサニピでも星見プロでも\nみんなのまとめ役をやってくれていますし、適任ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san‚ whether it's at Suny Peace or Hoshimi Prods.‚ You've always been\nthe one who brings everyone together‚ so you're the right person for the job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、年長者だからなんとなくそうなってるだけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ it's probably just because I'm the oldest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、遙子さんはコミュニケーション力があって\nチームをまとめるのがうまいと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ Haruko-san‚ you have excellent communication skills‚\nand you're good at leading a team.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "だから、サニピのみんなの意見や撮影スタッフの能力を\nうまく引き出せるって期待してるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I expect you to bring out the opinions of the Sunny Peace\nand the abilities of the filming staff effectively.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうかな？　持ち上げ過ぎだよ～\nでも、そこまで言われたら頑張っちゃおうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-is that so? You're praising me too much~\nBut if you put it that way‚ I guess I'll give it my all?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ぜひお願いします！　自信を持って下さい\n遙子さんは、今や大人気アイドルなんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ please do! Have confidence.\nHaruko-san‚ you're a hugely popular idol now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "私が大人気アイドル……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me‚ a hugely popular idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、デビュー当時とは比べものにならないくらい\nランキングは上がったけど……あんまり実感ないなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it's not even comparable to when I debuted.\nMy rankings have gone up‚ but… I don't really feel it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロには凄いアイドルが沢山いるから\n……今でも圧倒されちゃってるしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are so many amazing idols at Hoshimi Prods.\n…I'm still overwhelmed by it all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "現場に行けば、きっと実感出来ますよ\n今回の撮影は一流スタッフを厳選していますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you go to the stage‚ you'll definitely feel it.\nWe've carefully selected top-notch staff for this shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、そうだといいけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ I hope that's the case.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6266.6666667000045,
          "startTime": 106.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後、ジャケット撮影打ち合わせ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― The day of CD cover shoot after a few days",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "あの……{user}君\nちょっと、いい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… {user}.\nCan I ask you something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "あそこに座ってるサングラスの人って\n海外で活動してる凄いカメラマンさんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that person over there with sunglasses\nthe amazing photographer who works overseas?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "はい。普段はアメリカでアーティストのジャケットを\n中心にお仕事されてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ He normally works in the United States‚\nprimarily focusing on artist album covers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "超有名で多忙な人じゃない！？\nどうして日本にいるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't he incredibly famous and busy?\nWhy is he in Japan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "別件で帰国してたんですけど\nサニピの仕事も快く受けてくれたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He had returned for a different matter‚\nbut he also gladly accepted Sunny Peace's project.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "信じられない……\n――って、あそこで大声で笑ってる人、見たことある！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unbelievable…\n――Wait‚ I've seen that person over there‚ laughing loudly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、今年大ヒットした映画の舞台挨拶で……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ at the stage greeting of the blockbuster movie this year…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "新進気鋭のクリエイティブディレクターさんです\n今回の撮影に参加してくれることになりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He's a rising star in the world of creative directors.\nHe'll be joining us for this shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.9650808088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "二人ともサニピのファンだそうで、快諾してくれました\nしかもお二人とも遙子さんを推してるそうですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both of them are fans of Sunny Peace and readily accepted.\nAnd their favorite is you‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_05_01-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "私推し！？　……はー、なんだか嘘みたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They support me!? …Wow‚ it feels like a dream…",
        "id": ""
